item.title: CVE-2019-14820|2024-08-05T00:26:39.126Z -- keycloak -- keycloak
item.description: It was found that keycloak before version 8.0.0 exposes internal adapter endpoints in org.keycloak.constants.AdapterConstants, which can be invoked via a specially-crafted URL. This vulnerability could allow an attacker to access unauthorized information.
